♫ <i> The shadow left behind </i> ♫

612
00:42:40,524 --> 00:42:44,649
♫<i> Let's meet in the next life </i>♫

613
00:42:44,649 --> 00:42:48,299
♫<i> Even if it's just a handful of sand </i>♫

614
00:42:48,299 --> 00:42:52,575
♫<i> It's also a great moment </i>♫

615
00:43:03,110 --> 00:43:06,669
♫ <i>The heart gradually responds,</i> ♫

616
00:43:06,669 --> 00:43:09,009
♫ <i>gradually revives,</i> ♫

617
00:43:09,009 --> 00:43:12,429
♫ <i>gradually swims towards you</i> ♫

618
00:43:12,429 --> 00:43:16,669
♫ <i>Before bidding farewell,</i> ♫

619
00:43:16,669 --> 00:43:19,930
♫ <i>we expect an encounter</i> ♫

620
00:43:21,410 --> 00:43:25,249
♫ <i>As your silhouette weaves</i> ♫

621
00:43:25,249 --> 00:43:30,629
♫ <i>and locks in my nostalgic dream</i> ♫

622
00:43:30,629 --> 00:43:33,410
♫ <i>Before the daybreak,</i> ♫

623
00:43:33,410 --> 00:43:35,729
♫ <i>through the obsession of love,</i> ♫

624
00:43:35,729 --> 00:43:39,529
♫ <i>the yearning flowing through thoughts</i> ♫

625
00:43:39,530 --> 00:43:42,969
♫ <i>There's always a moment</i> ♫

626
